h4. Problem Definition

If a project contains many versions (over 3000), with many statuses associated with the project's workflow (over 100), the loading time of the Releases page becomes significantly slower. This cannot be reproduced with similar amount of versions, but with low number of statuses (ie. 3000 versions and below 10 statuses). Tested this on a vanilla instance, the former took around 24 seconds to load the releases page, while the latter only took around 4 seconds.

Example JQL query with many statuses when trying to load the Releases page:
